  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:14" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-subjectScheme-extension-upwards.dita.dita">You can broaden the scope of a subject category by creating a new subject scheme map
